<sub><italic>i</italic>−1</sub> and when <italic>z</italic>
<sub><italic>i</italic>−1</sub>=1, <italic>m</italic>
<sub><italic>i</italic></sub> is incremented by the normal random variable <italic>δ</italic>
<sub><italic>i</italic></sub> (<inline-formula id="IEq6"><alternatives><tex-math id="M15">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
